---
title: Mexican Chicken & Rice Bowls with Salsa Fresca & Lime Sour Cream
description: The beauty of a bowl-style dinner is the DIY element. This meal begins with aromatic yellow rice and Southwest-spiced chicken, all jazzed up with homemade salsa and a limey crema. When ready to build your bowl, feel free to go crazy with assembly. Crema on bottom! Rice on top of chicken! Hot sauce on everything!!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/61cb2b928e2ddc4eb77eebc2-34ed84b7.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/mexican-chicken-rice-bowls-61cb2b928e2ddc4eb77eebc2-d14e7d7e.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/mexican-chicken-and-rice-bowls-61cb2b928e2ddc4eb77eebc2
author: Michelle Doll Olson
course: main course
servings: 2
cuisine: Mexican
nutrition:
  calories: 710 kcal
  fat: 38 g
